&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the regex lib at C++ for the first time.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practice the C++ 11. E.g., copy_if, lambda.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
